      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0306回】　讓合氣道之「技」發揮效用</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0306-waza-effect-key/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0306-waza-effect-key/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
