    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0495回】　以「氣」結合</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0401-0500/t-0495-unite-with-ki/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
